<section name="Breezes of Confirmation" id="53">
  <quote id="1018">
    <introtext><![CDATA[]]></introtext>
	<text><![CDATA[...let your heart burn with loving kindness for all who may cross your path.]]></text>
 	<author><![CDATA[]]></author>
  	<reference><![CDATA[Breezes of Confirmation, p.9]]></reference>
    <language>en</language>
    <url><![CDATA[]]></url>
  </quote>
    <quote id="1019">
    <introtext><![CDATA[]]></introtext>
	<text><![CDATA[Ye were created to show love one to another...]]></text>
 	<author><![CDATA[]]></author>
  	<reference><![CDATA[Breezes of Confirmation, p.19]]></reference>
    <language>en</language>
    <url><![CDATA[]]></url>
  </quote>
    <quote id="1020">
    <introtext><![CDATA[]]></introtext>
	<text><![CDATA[Blessed is he who preferreth his brother before himself.]]></text>
 	<author><![CDATA[]]></author>
  	<reference><![CDATA[Breezes of Confirmation, p.19]]></reference>
    <language>en</language>
    <url><![CDATA[]]></url>
  </quote>
    <quote id="1021">
    <introtext><![CDATA[]]></introtext>
	<text><![CDATA[God is the helper of those souls whose aim is to serve humanity and whose efforts and endeavors are devoted to the good and betterment of all mankind.]]></text>
 	<author><![CDATA[]]></author>
  	<reference><![CDATA[Breezes of Confirmation, p.47]]></reference>
    <language>en</language>
    <url><![CDATA[]]></url>
  </quote>
    <quote id="1022">
    <introtext><![CDATA[]]></introtext>
	<text><![CDATA[Work done in the spirit of worship is the highest form of worship.]]></text>
 	<author><![CDATA[]]></author>
  	<reference><![CDATA[Breezes of Confirmation, p.54]]></reference>
    <language>en</language>
    <url><![CDATA[]]></url>
  </quote>
    <quote id="1023">
    <introtext><![CDATA[]]></introtext>
	<text><![CDATA[...make ye a mighty effort, and choose for yourselves a noble goal.]]></text>
 	<author><![CDATA[]]></author>
  	<reference><![CDATA[Breezes of Confirmation, p.72]]></reference>
    <language>en</language>
    <url><![CDATA[]]></url>
  </quote>
    <quote id="1024">
    <introtext><![CDATA[]]></introtext>
	<text><![CDATA[Make thou an effort that thou mayest take thy place under the sun and receive an abundant share of its dazzling light.]]></text>
 	<author><![CDATA[]]></author>
  	<reference><![CDATA[Breezes of Confirmation, p.78]]></reference>
    <language>en</language>
    <url><![CDATA[]]></url>
  </quote>
